  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of <strong>SurvAIval</strong>, where survival meets automation! Gather resources, build your base, and bring it to life with the power of <strong>AI</strong>. Start small by crushing materials to earn money, but soon, your <strong>AI</strong> creations will handle the grind for you, freeing you to explore uncharted lands, conquer new territories, and forge alliances with those in need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your empire, meet the demands of new allies, and defend your base against relentless goblin raids. Will you rise as a master of automation and survival, or will the chaos of the world overtake you? The future of your base is in your hands!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather, collect, and manage resources efficiently.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create <strong>AI</strong>s to assist you in your survival journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your base from the ground up and defend it against threats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new areas to explore and expand your domain.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and upgrade your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set your own goals and forge your unique path to success. Achieve whatever you aspire to!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock New Characters</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/0db62a73e8659eb077ab689f8e491322.avif?t=1758634482\" width=512 height=256 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create AIs To Do Your Work</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/fb999caa060ba8718982f2f6f7bc7f86.avif?t=1758634482\" width=512 height=256 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade Your AIs</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/29bd6e526e7744465d37b9b9e26d5d2d.avif?t=1758634482\" width=512 height=256 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Base</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/6fafefe38fccc6475c77244119ef9017.avif?t=1758634482\" width=512 height=256 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the World</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/8ac25cde8adb1e5b76c1f9034b3c9f95.avif?t=1758634482\" width=512 height=256 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Escape The Dungeon</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/aaff51264b504861731589d7ea1007f5.avif?t=1758634482\" width=512 height=256 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>In Game Footage</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/d8e1abb41d596243be3bb8e6c79b635e.poster.avif?t=1758634482\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/d8e1abb41d596243be3bb8e6c79b635e.webm?t=1758634482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391060/extras/d8e1abb41d596243be3bb8e6c79b635e.mp4?t=1758634482\" type=\"video